    "description": "If you're a passionate Guest Relations Manager with drive and ambition, Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions in Rajkot is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions:\nAnanda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ananda in the Himalayas Ventures Solutions!",
